metadata.name: HEY COLLECTOR KISS MY ASS
metadata.description:
While creators enter the NFT space with their hearts open and ready to rock, the daily grind with all the collector<->creator dynamics and hustling kinda kills the vibe and sucks the energy.

Editions is a reminder to all in the spirit of good old punk rock and love for adventure based on the grounding works of the masters in the space. I chose the most hyped medium to spread the message. 

Collectors and Creators! I conjure you not to let the kids inside yall turn into clerks and white collars.

I charge you to disrupt the NFT space with thy works. I charge you to ingest thy fresh blood into the space to give it a new life.

Grab a piece of freedom for as little as 0.01 on Manifold with blessings from Don Ivanio attached to it. Let's rock fellas!

This pork will only be available for 48 hours
